"{\"uid\": \"si.com-fannation-sneakers-news-snoop-dogg-unveils-special-skechers-sneakers-for-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Snoop Dogg is one of the most famous people in the world.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 57, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From multi-platinum hits, television shows, films, and numerous other entrepreneurial endeavors, the hip-hop icon has proven that he can do it all.\", \"from\": 58, \"to\": 205, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With his imprint now in the sneaker world, Snoop is expanding his partnership with Skechers with a collection of custom sneakers that he has unveiled before he is the official torchbearer and broadcast commentator at the 2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 207, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 290, \"end\": 298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skechers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Skechers\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skechers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skechers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSkechers x Snoop Dogg Paris Olympics\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d collection, \\u00c2\\u00a0which was curated by the Skechers x Snoop Dogg design team, will come in five colorways.\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 468, \"end\": 478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}, {\"begin\": 479, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998017302, \"rank\": 1.9830990316132996e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 536, \"end\": 544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skechers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Skechers\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skechers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skechers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The shoes come equipped with \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cEaster eggs\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d on each pair including Snoop\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s quote, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009c I only compete with myself\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d on the soles and medal-themed gold, silver, and bronze touches on and around the laces.\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 808, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is an all-white silhouette with gold trim and a red, white, and blue flag on the tongue of the sneaker.\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paying homage to hip-hop, the graffiti silhouette has \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cParis\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d on the side of the shoe and comes with red, white, and blue shoelaces.\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 1056, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another silhouette features an eye-catching paisley pattern with red, white, and blue accents.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1152, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The shoes come with gold embellishments that represent Snoop\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s one-of-a-kind style.\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1238, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lastly, the all-gold everything silhouette is crafted from premium, snake-embossed gold leather, and the high-top style is emblazoned with Snoop\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Paris-inspired logo.\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1409, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since Snoop first made his first appearance in Skechers The Comfort Technology Company's 2023 Big Game campaign and the announcement of the Skechers x Snoop Dogg collaboration in August of the same year, Snoop has been rocking his kicks everywhere he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s been spotted proudly touting the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098S\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 logo on his feet.\\u00c2  As an ambassador of the brand \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 especially its patentedSkechers Hands Free Slip-ins\\u00c2\\u00ae technology\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 the legendary rapper\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s footwear collection will include sneakers and lifestyle shoes for men and women, performance basketball shoes, and music more.\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1458, \"end\": 1466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skechers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.841333900895933e-42, \"text\": \"Skechers\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skechers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skechers\"}, {\"begin\": 1551, \"end\": 1559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skechers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Skechers\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skechers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skechers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Be sure to stay tapped intoSports Illustratedfor all your footwear news from the sports world and beyond.\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Further Reading:LeBron James debuted the Nike LeBron 22 in a Team USA practice.\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2105, \"end\": 2117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LeBron James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 2150, \"end\":